62 bool ConstraintSet::Bind (const Model &model) {
63  assert (bound == false);
64 
65  if (bound) {
66  std::cerr << "Error: binding an already bound constraint set!" << std::endl;
67  abort();
68  }
69  unsigned int n_constr = size();
70 
71  H.conservativeResize (model.dof_count, model.dof_count);
72  H.setZero();
73  C.conservativeResize (model.dof_count);
74  C.setZero();
75  gamma.conservativeResize (n_constr);
76  gamma.setZero();
77  G.conservativeResize (n_constr, model.dof_count);
78  G.setZero();
79  A.conservativeResize (model.dof_count + n_constr, model.dof_count + n_constr);
80  A.setZero();
81  b.conservativeResize (model.dof_count + n_constr);
82  b.setZero();
83  x.conservativeResize (model.dof_count + n_constr);
84  x.setZero();
85 
86 #ifdef RBDL_USE_SIMPLE_MATH
87  GT_qr = SimpleMath::HouseholderQR<Math::MatrixNd> (G.transpose());
88 #else
89  GT_qr = Eigen::HouseholderQR<Math::MatrixNd> (G.transpose());
90 #endif
91  GT_qr_Q = MatrixNd::Zero (model.dof_count, model.dof_count);
92  Y = MatrixNd::Zero (model.dof_count, G.rows());
93  Z = MatrixNd::Zero (model.dof_count, model.dof_count - G.rows());
94  qddot_y = VectorNd::Zero (model.dof_count);
95  qddot_z = VectorNd::Zero (model.dof_count);
96 
97  K.conservativeResize (n_constr, n_constr);
98  K.setZero();
99  a.conservativeResize (n_constr);
100  a.setZero();
101  QDDot_t.conservativeResize (model.dof_count);
102  QDDot_t.setZero();
103  QDDot_0.conservativeResize (model.dof_count);
104  QDDot_0.setZero();
105  f_t.resize (n_constr, SpatialVectorZero);
106  f_ext_constraints.resize (model.mBodies.size(), SpatialVectorZero);
107  point_accel_0.resize (n_constr, Vector3d::Zero());
108 
109  d_pA = std::vector<SpatialVector> (model.mBodies.size(), SpatialVectorZero);
110  d_a = std::vector<SpatialVector> (model.mBodies.size(), SpatialVectorZero);
111  d_u = VectorNd::Zero (model.mBodies.size());
112 
113  d_IA = std::vector<SpatialMatrix> (model.mBodies.size(), SpatialMatrixIdentity);
114  d_U = std::vector<SpatialVector> (model.mBodies.size(), SpatialVectorZero);
115  d_d = VectorNd::Zero (model.mBodies.size());
116 
117  d_multdof3_u = std::vector<Math::Vector3d> (model.mBodies.size(), Math::Vector3d::Zero());
118 
119  bound = true;
120 
121  return bound;
122 }

161 RBDL_DLLAPI void SolveContactSystemDirect (
162  Math::MatrixNd &H,
163  const Math::MatrixNd &G,
164  const Math::VectorNd &c,
165  const Math::VectorNd &gamma,
166  Math::VectorNd &qddot,
167  Math::VectorNd &lambda,
168  Math::MatrixNd &A,
169  Math::VectorNd &b,
170  Math::VectorNd &x,
171  Math::LinearSolver &linear_solver
172  ) {
173  // Build the system: Copy H
174  A.block(0, 0, c.rows(), c.rows()) = H;
175 
176  // Copy G and G^T
177  A.block(0, c.rows(), c.rows(), gamma.rows()) = G.transpose();
178  A.block(c.rows(), 0, gamma.rows(), c.rows()) = G;
179 
180  // Build the system: Copy -C + \tau
181  b.block(0, 0, c.rows(), 1) = c;
182  b.block(c.rows(), 0, gamma.rows(), 1) = gamma;
183 
184  LOG << "A = " << std::endl << A << std::endl;
185  LOG << "b = " << std::endl << b << std::endl;
186 
187  switch (linear_solver) {
188  case (LinearSolverPartialPivLU) :
189 #ifdef RBDL_USE_SIMPLE_MATH
190  // SimpleMath does not have a LU solver so just use its QR solver
191  x = A.householderQr().solve(b);
192 #else
193  x = A.partialPivLu().solve(b);
194 #endif
195  break;
196  case (LinearSolverColPivHouseholderQR) :
197  x = A.colPivHouseholderQr().solve(b);
198  break;
199  case (LinearSolverHouseholderQR) :
200  x = A.householderQr().solve(b);
201  break;
202  default:
203  LOG << "Error: Invalid linear solver: " << linear_solver << std::endl;
204  assert (0);
205  break;
206  }
207 
208  LOG << "x = " << std::endl << x << std::endl;
209 }

211 RBDL_DLLAPI void SolveContactSystemRangeSpaceSparse (
212  Model &model,
213  Math::MatrixNd &H,
214  const Math::MatrixNd &G,
215  const Math::VectorNd &c,
216  const Math::VectorNd &gamma,
217  Math::VectorNd &qddot,
218  Math::VectorNd &lambda,
219  Math::MatrixNd &K,
220  Math::VectorNd &a,
221  Math::LinearSolver linear_solver
222  ) {
223  SparseFactorizeLTL (model, H);
224 
225  MatrixNd Y (G.transpose());
226 
227  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < Y.cols(); i++) {
228  VectorNd Y_col = Y.block(0,i,Y.rows(),1);
229  SparseSolveLTx (model, H, Y_col);
230  Y.block(0,i,Y.rows(),1) = Y_col;
231  }
232 
233  VectorNd z (c);
234  SparseSolveLTx (model, H, z);
235 
236  K = Y.transpose() * Y;
237 
238  a = gamma - Y.transpose() * z;
239 
240  lambda = K.llt().solve(a);
241 
242  qddot = c + G.transpose() * lambda;
243  SparseSolveLTx (model, H, qddot);
244  SparseSolveLx (model, H, qddot);
245 }

247 RBDL_DLLAPI
248 void SolveContactSystemNullSpace (
249  Math::MatrixNd &H,
250  const Math::MatrixNd &G,
251  const Math::VectorNd &c,
252  const Math::VectorNd &gamma,
253  Math::VectorNd &qddot,
254  Math::VectorNd &lambda,
255  Math::MatrixNd &Y,
256  Math::MatrixNd &Z,
257  Math::VectorNd &qddot_y,
258  Math::VectorNd &qddot_z,
259  Math::LinearSolver &linear_solver
260  ) {
261  switch (linear_solver) {
262  case (LinearSolverPartialPivLU) :
263 #ifdef RBDL_USE_SIMPLE_MATH
264  // SimpleMath does not have a LU solver so just use its QR solver
265  qddot_y = (G * Y).householderQr().solve (gamma);
266 #else
267  qddot_y = (G * Y).partialPivLu().solve (gamma);
268 #endif
269  break;
270  case (LinearSolverColPivHouseholderQR) :
271  qddot_y = (G * Y).colPivHouseholderQr().solve (gamma);
272  break;
273  case (LinearSolverHouseholderQR) :
274  qddot_y = (G * Y).householderQr().solve (gamma);
275  break;
276  default:
277  LOG << "Error: Invalid linear solver: " << linear_solver << std::endl;
278  assert (0);
279  break;
280  }
281 
282  qddot_z = (Z.transpose() * H * Z).llt().solve(Z.transpose() * (c - H * Y * qddot_y));
283 
284  qddot = Y * qddot_y + Z * qddot_z;
285 
286  switch (linear_solver) {
287  case (LinearSolverPartialPivLU) :
288 #ifdef RBDL_USE_SIMPLE_MATH
289  // SimpleMath does not have a LU solver so just use its QR solver
290  qddot_y = (G * Y).householderQr().solve (gamma);
291 #else
292  lambda = (G * Y).partialPivLu().solve (Y.transpose() * (H * qddot - c));
293 #endif
294  break;
295  case (LinearSolverColPivHouseholderQR) :
296  lambda = (G * Y).colPivHouseholderQr().solve (Y.transpose() * (H * qddot - c));
297  break;
298  case (LinearSolverHouseholderQR) :
299  lambda = (G * Y).householderQr().solve (Y.transpose() * (H * qddot - c));
300  break;
301  default:
302  LOG << "Error: Invalid linear solver: " << linear_solver << std::endl;
303  assert (0);
304  break;
305  }
306 }

308 RBDL_DLLAPI
309 void CalcContactJacobian(
310  Model &model,
311  const Math::VectorNd &Q,
312  const ConstraintSet &CS,
313  Math::MatrixNd &G,
314  bool update_kinematics
315  ) {
316  if (update_kinematics)
317  UpdateKinematicsCustom (model, &Q, NULL, NULL);
318 
319  unsigned int i,j;
320 
321  // variables to check whether we need to recompute G
322  unsigned int prev_body_id = 0;
323  Vector3d prev_body_point = Vector3d::Zero();
324  MatrixNd Gi (3, model.dof_count);
325 
326  for (i = 0; i < CS.size(); i++) {
327  // only compute the matrix Gi if actually needed
328  if (prev_body_id != CS.body[i] || prev_body_point != CS.point[i]) {
329  Gi.setZero();
330  CalcPointJacobian (model, Q, CS.body[i], CS.point[i], Gi, false);
331  prev_body_id = CS.body[i];
332  prev_body_point = CS.point[i];
333  }
334 
335  for (j = 0; j < model.dof_count; j++) {
336  Vector3d gaxis (Gi(0,j), Gi(1,j), Gi(2,j));
337  G(i,j) = gaxis.transpose() * CS.normal[i];
338  }
339  }
340 }

342 RBDL_DLLAPI
343 void CalcContactSystemVariables (
344  Model &model,
345  const Math::VectorNd &Q,
346  const Math::VectorNd &QDot,
347  const Math::VectorNd &Tau,
348  ConstraintSet &CS
349  ) {
350  // Compute C
351  NonlinearEffects (model, Q, QDot, CS.C);
352  assert (CS.H.cols() == model.dof_count && CS.H.rows() == model.dof_count);
353 
354  // Compute H
355  CompositeRigidBodyAlgorithm (model, Q, CS.H, false);
356 
357  // Compute G
358  // We have to update model.X_base as they are not automatically computed
359  // by NonlinearEffects()
360  for (unsigned int i = 1; i < model.mBodies.size(); i++) {
361  model.X_base[i] = model.X_lambda[i] * model.X_base[model.lambda[i]];
362  }
363  CalcContactJacobian (model, Q, CS, CS.G, false);
364 
365  // Compute gamma
366  unsigned int prev_body_id = 0;
367  Vector3d prev_body_point = Vector3d::Zero();
368  Vector3d gamma_i = Vector3d::Zero();
369 
370  CS.QDDot_0.setZero();
371  UpdateKinematicsCustom (model, NULL, NULL, &CS.QDDot_0);
372 
373  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < CS.size(); i++) {
374  // only compute point accelerations when necessary
375  if (prev_body_id != CS.body[i] || prev_body_point != CS.point[i]) {
376  gamma_i = CalcPointAcceleration (model, Q, QDot, CS.QDDot_0, CS.body[i], CS.point[i], false);
377  prev_body_id = CS.body[i];
378  prev_body_point = CS.point[i];
379  }
380 
381  // we also substract ContactData[i].acceleration such that the contact
382  // point will have the desired acceleration
383  CS.gamma[i] = CS.acceleration[i] - CS.normal[i].dot(gamma_i);
384  }
385 }

529 RBDL_DLLAPI
530 void ForwardDynamicsApplyConstraintForces (
531  Model &model,
532  const VectorNd &Tau,
533  ConstraintSet &CS,
534  VectorNd &QDDot
535  ) {
536  LOG << "-------- " << __func__ << " --------" << std::endl;
537  assert (QDDot.size() == model.dof_count);
538 
539  unsigned int i = 0;
540 
541  for (i = 1; i < model.mBodies.size(); i++) {
542  model.IA[i] = model.I[i].toMatrix();;
543  model.pA[i] = crossf(model.v[i],model.I[i] * model.v[i]);
544 
545  if (CS.f_ext_constraints[i] != SpatialVectorZero) {
546  LOG << "External force (" << i << ") = " << model.X_base[i].toMatrixAdjoint() * CS.f_ext_constraints[i] << std::endl;
547  model.pA[i] -= model.X_base[i].toMatrixAdjoint() * CS.f_ext_constraints[i];
548  }
549  }
550 
551  // ClearLogOutput();
552 
553  LOG << "--- first loop ---" << std::endl;
554 
555  for (i = model.mBodies.size() - 1; i > 0; i--) {
556  unsigned int q_index = model.mJoints[i].q_index;
557 
558  if (model.mJoints[i].mDoFCount == 3
559  && model.mJoints[i].mJointType != JointTypeCustom) {
560  unsigned int lambda = model.lambda[i];
561  model.multdof3_u[i] = Vector3d (Tau[q_index],
562  Tau[q_index + 1],
563  Tau[q_index + 2])
564  - model.multdof3_S[i].transpose() * model.pA[i];
565 
566  if (lambda != 0) {
567  SpatialMatrix Ia = model.IA[i] - (model.multdof3_U[i]
568  * model.multdof3_Dinv[i]
569  * model.multdof3_U[i].transpose());
570 
571  SpatialVector pa = model.pA[i] + Ia * model.c[i]
572  + model.multdof3_U[i] * model.multdof3_Dinv[i] * model.multdof3_u[i];
573 
574 #ifdef EIGEN_CORE_H
575  model.IA[lambda].noalias() += (model.X_lambda[i].toMatrixTranspose()
576  * Ia * model.X_lambda[i].toMatrix());
577  model.pA[lambda].noalias() += model.X_lambda[i].applyTranspose(pa);
578 #else
579  model.IA[lambda] += (model.X_lambda[i].toMatrixTranspose()
580  * Ia * model.X_lambda[i].toMatrix());
581  model.pA[lambda] += model.X_lambda[i].applyTranspose(pa);
582 #endif
583  LOG << "pA[" << lambda << "] = " << model.pA[lambda].transpose()
584  << std::endl;
585  }
586  } else if (model.mJoints[i].mDoFCount == 1
587  && model.mJoints[i].mJointType != JointTypeCustom) {
588  model.u[i] = Tau[q_index] - model.S[i].dot(model.pA[i]);
589 
590  unsigned int lambda = model.lambda[i];
591  if (lambda != 0) {
592  SpatialMatrix Ia = model.IA[i]
593  - model.U[i] * (model.U[i] / model.d[i]).transpose();
594  SpatialVector pa = model.pA[i] + Ia * model.c[i]
595  + model.U[i] * model.u[i] / model.d[i];
596 #ifdef EIGEN_CORE_H
597  model.IA[lambda].noalias() += (model.X_lambda[i].toMatrixTranspose()
598  * Ia * model.X_lambda[i].toMatrix());
599  model.pA[lambda].noalias() += model.X_lambda[i].applyTranspose(pa);
600 #else
601  model.IA[lambda] += (model.X_lambda[i].toMatrixTranspose()
602  * Ia * model.X_lambda[i].toMatrix());
603  model.pA[lambda] += model.X_lambda[i].applyTranspose(pa);
604 #endif
605  LOG << "pA[" << lambda << "] = "
606  << model.pA[lambda].transpose() << std::endl;
607  }
608  } else if(model.mJoints[i].mJointType == JointTypeCustom) {
609 
610  unsigned int kI = model.mJoints[i].custom_joint_index;
611  unsigned int dofI = model.mCustomJoints[kI]->mDoFCount;
612  unsigned int lambda = model.lambda[i];
613  VectorNd tau_temp = VectorNd::Zero(dofI);
614 
615  for(int z=0; z<dofI;++z){
616  tau_temp[z] = Tau[q_index+z];
617  }
618 
619  model.mCustomJoints[kI]->u = tau_temp
620  - (model.mCustomJoints[kI]->S.transpose()
621  * model.pA[i]);
622 
623  if (lambda != 0) {
624  SpatialMatrix Ia = model.IA[i]
625  - ( model.mCustomJoints[kI]->U
626  * model.mCustomJoints[kI]->Dinv
627  * model.mCustomJoints[kI]->U.transpose());

630  + ( model.mCustomJoints[kI]->U
631  * model.mCustomJoints[kI]->Dinv
632  * model.mCustomJoints[kI]->u);
633 #ifdef EIGEN_CORE_H
634  model.IA[lambda].noalias() += model.X_lambda[i].toMatrixTranspose()
635  * Ia * model.X_lambda[i].toMatrix();

637  model.pA[lambda].noalias() += model.X_lambda[i].applyTranspose(pa);
638 #else

641 
642  model.pA[lambda] += model.X_lambda[i].applyTranspose(pa);
643 #endif
644  LOG << "pA[" << lambda << "] = " << model.pA[lambda].transpose()
645  << std::endl;
646  }
647  }
648  }
649 
650  model.a[0] = SpatialVector (0., 0., 0., -model.gravity[0], -model.gravity[1], -model.gravity[2]);
651 
652  for (i = 1; i < model.mBodies.size(); i++) {
653  unsigned int q_index = model.mJoints[i].q_index;
654  unsigned int lambda = model.lambda[i];
655  SpatialTransform X_lambda = model.X_lambda[i];
656 
657  model.a[i] = X_lambda.apply(model.a[lambda]) + model.c[i];
658  LOG << "a'[" << i << "] = " << model.a[i].transpose() << std::endl;
659 
660  if (model.mJoints[i].mDoFCount == 3
661  && model.mJoints[i].mJointType != JointTypeCustom) {
662  Vector3d qdd_temp = model.multdof3_Dinv[i] *
663  (model.multdof3_u[i]
664  - model.multdof3_U[i].transpose() * model.a[i]);
665 
666  QDDot[q_index] = qdd_temp[0];
667  QDDot[q_index + 1] = qdd_temp[1];
668  QDDot[q_index + 2] = qdd_temp[2];
669  model.a[i] = model.a[i] + model.multdof3_S[i] * qdd_temp;
670  } else if (model.mJoints[i].mDoFCount == 1
671  && model.mJoints[i].mJointType != JointTypeCustom) {
672  QDDot[q_index] = (1./model.d[i]) * (model.u[i] - model.U[i].dot(model.a[i]));
673  model.a[i] = model.a[i] + model.S[i] * QDDot[q_index];
674  } else if (model.mJoints[i].mJointType == JointTypeCustom){
675  unsigned int kI = model.mJoints[i].custom_joint_index;
676  unsigned int dofI = model.mCustomJoints[kI]->mDoFCount;
677  VectorNd qdd_temp = VectorNd::Zero(dofI);
678 
679  qdd_temp = model.mCustomJoints[kI]->Dinv
680  * (model.mCustomJoints[kI]->u
681  - model.mCustomJoints[kI]->U.transpose()
682  * model.a[i]);
683 
684  for(int z=0; z<dofI;++z){
685  QDDot[q_index+z] = qdd_temp[z];
686  }
687 
688  model.a[i] = model.a[i] + (model.mCustomJoints[kI]->S * qdd_temp);
689  }
690  }
691 
692  LOG << "QDDot = " << QDDot.transpose() << std::endl;
693 }

819  }

823  }

835 RBDL_DLLAPI
836 void ForwardDynamicsContactsKokkevis (
837  Model &model,
838  const VectorNd &Q,
839  const VectorNd &QDot,
840  const VectorNd &Tau,
841  ConstraintSet &CS,
842  VectorNd &QDDot
843  ) {
844  LOG << "-------- " << __func__ << " ------" << std::endl;
845 
846  assert (CS.f_ext_constraints.size() == model.mBodies.size());
847  assert (CS.QDDot_0.size() == model.dof_count);
848  assert (CS.QDDot_t.size() == model.dof_count);
849  assert (CS.f_t.size() == CS.size());
850  assert (CS.point_accel_0.size() == CS.size());
851  assert (CS.K.rows() == CS.size());
852  assert (CS.K.cols() == CS.size());
853  assert (CS.force.size() == CS.size());
854  assert (CS.a.size() == CS.size());
855 
856  Vector3d point_accel_t;
857 
858  unsigned int ci = 0;
859 
860  // The default acceleration only needs to be computed once
861  {
862  SUPPRESS_LOGGING;
863  ForwardDynamics (model, Q, QDot, Tau, CS.QDDot_0);
864  }
865 
866  LOG << "=== Initial Loop Start ===" << std::endl;
867  // we have to compute the standard accelerations first as we use them to
868  // compute the effects of each test force
869  for (ci = 0; ci < CS.size(); ci++) {
870  unsigned int body_id = CS.body[ci];
871  Vector3d point = CS.point[ci];
872  Vector3d normal = CS.normal[ci];
873  double acceleration = CS.acceleration[ci];
874 
875  LOG << "body_id = " << body_id << std::endl;
876  LOG << "point = " << point << std::endl;
877  LOG << "normal = " << normal << std::endl;
878  LOG << "QDDot_0 = " << CS.QDDot_0.transpose() << std::endl;
879  {
880  SUPPRESS_LOGGING;
881  UpdateKinematicsCustom (model, NULL, NULL, &CS.QDDot_0);
882  CS.point_accel_0[ci] = CalcPointAcceleration (model, Q, QDot, CS.QDDot_0, body_id, point, false);
883 
884  CS.a[ci] = - acceleration + normal.dot(CS.point_accel_0[ci]);
885  }
886  LOG << "point_accel_0 = " << CS.point_accel_0[ci].transpose();
887  }
888 
889  // Now we can compute and apply the test forces and use their net effect
890  // to compute the inverse articlated inertia to fill K.
891  for (ci = 0; ci < CS.size(); ci++) {
892  LOG << "=== Testforce Loop Start ===" << std::endl;
893  unsigned int body_id = CS.body[ci];
894  Vector3d point = CS.point[ci];
895  Vector3d normal = CS.normal[ci];
896 
897  unsigned int movable_body_id = body_id;
898  if (model.IsFixedBodyId(body_id)) {
899  unsigned int fbody_id = body_id - model.fixed_body_discriminator;
900  movable_body_id = model.mFixedBodies[fbody_id].mMovableParent;
901  }
902 
903  // assemble the test force
904  LOG << "normal = " << normal.transpose() << std::endl;
905 
906  Vector3d point_global = CalcBodyToBaseCoordinates (model, Q, body_id, point, false);
907  LOG << "point_global = " << point_global.transpose() << std::endl;
908 
909  CS.f_t[ci] = SpatialTransform (Matrix3d::Identity(), -point_global).applyAdjoint (SpatialVector (0., 0., 0., -normal[0], -normal[1], -normal[2]));
910  CS.f_ext_constraints[movable_body_id] = CS.f_t[ci];
911  LOG << "f_t[" << movable_body_id << "] = " << CS.f_t[ci].transpose() << std::endl;
912 
913  {
914  // SUPPRESS_LOGGING;
915  ForwardDynamicsAccelerationDeltas (model, CS, CS.QDDot_t, movable_body_id, CS.f_ext_constraints);
916  LOG << "QDDot_0 = " << CS.QDDot_0.transpose() << std::endl;
917  LOG << "QDDot_t = " << (CS.QDDot_t + CS.QDDot_0).transpose() << std::endl;
918  LOG << "QDDot_t - QDDot_0= " << (CS.QDDot_t).transpose() << std::endl;
919  }
920 
921  CS.f_ext_constraints[movable_body_id].setZero();
922 
923  CS.QDDot_t += CS.QDDot_0;
924 
925  // compute the resulting acceleration
926  {
927  SUPPRESS_LOGGING;
928  UpdateKinematicsCustom (model, NULL, NULL, &CS.QDDot_t);
929  }
930 
931  for (unsigned int cj = 0; cj < CS.size(); cj++) {
932  {
933  SUPPRESS_LOGGING;
934 
935  point_accel_t = CalcPointAcceleration (model, Q, QDot, CS.QDDot_t, CS.body[cj], CS.point[cj], false);
936  }
937 
938  LOG << "point_accel_0 = " << CS.point_accel_0[ci].transpose() << std::endl;
939  CS.K(ci,cj) = CS.normal[cj].dot(point_accel_t - CS.point_accel_0[cj]);
940  LOG << "point_accel_t = " << point_accel_t.transpose() << std::endl;
941  }
942  }
943 
944  LOG << "K = " << std::endl << CS.K << std::endl;
945  LOG << "a = " << std::endl << CS.a << std::endl;
946 
947 #ifndef RBDL_USE_SIMPLE_MATH
948  switch (CS.linear_solver) {
949  case (LinearSolverPartialPivLU) :
950  CS.force = CS.K.partialPivLu().solve(CS.a);
951  break;
952  case (LinearSolverColPivHouseholderQR) :
953  CS.force = CS.K.colPivHouseholderQr().solve(CS.a);
954  break;
955  case (LinearSolverHouseholderQR) :
956  CS.force = CS.K.householderQr().solve(CS.a);
957  break;
958  default:
959  LOG << "Error: Invalid linear solver: " << CS.linear_solver << std::endl;
960  assert (0);
961  break;
962  }
963 #else
964  bool solve_successful = LinSolveGaussElimPivot (CS.K, CS.a, CS.force);
965  assert (solve_successful);
966 #endif
967 
968  LOG << "f = " << CS.force.transpose() << std::endl;
969 
970  for (ci = 0; ci < CS.size(); ci++) {
971  unsigned int body_id = CS.body[ci];
972  unsigned int movable_body_id = body_id;
973 
974  if (model.IsFixedBodyId(body_id)) {
975  unsigned int fbody_id = body_id - model.fixed_body_discriminator;
976  movable_body_id = model.mFixedBodies[fbody_id].mMovableParent;
977  }
978 
979  CS.f_ext_constraints[movable_body_id] -= CS.f_t[ci] * CS.force[ci];
980  LOG << "f_ext[" << movable_body_id << "] = "
981  << CS.f_ext_constraints[movable_body_id].transpose() << std::endl;
982  }
983 
984  {
985  SUPPRESS_LOGGING;
986  ForwardDynamicsApplyConstraintForces (model, Tau, CS, QDDot);
987  }
988 
989  LOG << "QDDot after applying f_ext: " << QDDot.transpose() << std::endl;
990 }
